--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This role manages minicom.

Minicom is a simple text-based modem control and terminal emulation program
somewhat similar to MSDOS Telix. Minicom includes a dialing directory, full
ANSI and VT100 emulation, an (external) scripting language, and other features.

For more detailed information on the usage and available configuration options
please consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: minicom
       minicom_state: 'install'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: minicom
       minicom_state: 'remove'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VARIABLES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLE
  minicom_state
    Specify predetermined 'minicom_state' variable (string).

    Install: 'true' | 'yes' | 'install'
    Remove : 'false' | 'no' | 'remove'
    Default: 'install'

